			<h4><a id="comment_link_64137358" name="comment_link_64137358" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23184254&amp;cid=64137358" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64137358)" >Re:Part of the early 2000s XML solves everything</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64137358" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64137358); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~slack_justyb">slack_justyb</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~slack_justyb">( 862874 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64137358">		
		on Saturday January 06, 2024 @06:22PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23184254&amp;cid=64137358">#64137358</a>)
